Idea:- For solving this question in one pass we can use two pointer approach. In this approach we make two pointer and maintain a gap of size n-1 between these two pointers. 
When first pointer is at the end of the list we sure that second pointer at n+1 position from end . Now we need only remove nth element with the help of second pointer.
The Only edge case is when (n==size of list).
